Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.02,0:00:31.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:31.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.99,0:00:39.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:39.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.28,0:00:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.54,0:00:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.25,0:00:54.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
