Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.24,0:01:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.24,0:01:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.41,0:01:17.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:17.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.53,0:01:18.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:18.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.49,0:01:21.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给小蜗搬这一大袋的蜗牛粮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:21.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carrying this heavy bag of snail food for Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.16,0:01:22.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗最近怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:22.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How is Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.91,0:01:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's fine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.08,0:01:26.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  能不能待会再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:26.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, can we talk about this some other time?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.29,0:01:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蜗牛粮真的太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This snail food is really heavy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.92,0:01:29.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:29.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.84,0:01:32.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我有事要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:32.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But there was something I wanted to tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something important
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚是在跟谁讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who was I talking to?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看这是个什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, Captain, what have we here?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.35,0:01:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是封小小的格式信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a tiny form letter
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.90,0:01:53.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的先生或者女士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:53.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dear Sir or Ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.15,0:01:55.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我们错过您了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:55.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are sorry we missed you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.86,0:02:00.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会尽快再次为您寄送包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:58.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We will attempt to re-deliver your package
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,at our earliest convenience
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.49,0:02:02.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:02.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.04,0:02:04.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:04.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My package
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.54,0:02:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看下收到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see what we got here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(812,170)}美人鱼战士与企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.00,0:02:15.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士与企鹅男孩官方球拍组
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My official Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,paddleball set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:15.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(542,156)}官方球拍组
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:15.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(442,776)}尼克公司
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快接受肮脏泡泡的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take the Dirty Bubble Challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.81,0:02:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连续拍球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit the paddleball
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.77,0:02:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,29998559671349下不中断
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,29,998,559,671,349 times in a row
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.23,0:02:38.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡  无论你漂浮在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:38.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dirty Bubble, wherever you float
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.65,0:02:41.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特此接受你的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:41.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hereby accept your challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.46,0:02:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.21,0:02:56.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:56.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.17,0:02:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.63,0:03:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:10.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1194,916)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.12,0:03:25.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:25.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.70,0:03:28.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:28.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.75,0:03:35.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  原来害我分心的声音是你发的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:35.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, that distracting sound came from you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  我没办法跟你一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I can't play with you right now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Man needs me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我可求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, please
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正努力打败肮脏泡泡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to defeat the Dirty Bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先让我弄清楚  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, let's get this straight, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不想要我打败肮脏泡泡是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't want me to defeat the Dirty Bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要知道肮脏泡泡可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Dirty Bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七大洋里的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,terror of the seven seas
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,专门对付我最爱的电视超级英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:00.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,arch nemesis of my favorite TV superheroes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美人鱼战士和企鹅男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很明显还是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and apparently
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知名的拍球冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,renowned paddleball champion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,384)}球拍组
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少我认识到了这个任务有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I for one, recognize the importance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:09.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of this undertaking
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你有没有认识到  我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But whether or not you do remains to be seen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话  我要继续挑战了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, if you don't mind, I would like to get back to it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pets
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.46,0:04:22.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候真不知道它们听不听得懂人话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I wonder if
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they understand a word you're saying
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我不喜欢你这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, I hate it when you do that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.60,0:04:35.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你的主人完成这项重要的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:35.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And leave your master to his important affairs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拍一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏泡泡  去死吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dirty Bubble, say your prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:12.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(234,450)}离开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(692,746)}蜗牛快车
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经好几天没见到海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen SpongeBob in a couple days
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他等下一定会很高兴能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll be glad to know
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我记起来要跟他说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember what I wanted to tell him
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's strange
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.39,0:05:57.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平常我都用这只手敲门的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:57.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Usually, I knock on the with this hand
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.98,0:05:58.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:58.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You around?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.73,0:06:02.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:02.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.15,0:06:06.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:06.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.15,0:06:08.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:08.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034,202)}海绵宝宝的厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.99,0:06:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.21,0:06:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.17,0:06:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这幅画给挂歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This picture is crooked
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:28.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.64,0:06:31.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:31.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我接受了肮脏泡泡的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I took the Dirty Bubble challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You what?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么哭了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.98,0:06:44.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哭是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:44.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,many years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我接受了那场挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I took that challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.86,0:06:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后来怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:52.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过发过来的奖杯让我给丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then I lost the trophy they sent me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You lost the
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.79,0:07:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吃点海草饼干配海马奶喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's have some kelp cookies and seahorse milk
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.38,0:07:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我每次丢东西都会那样解闷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that always cheers me up when I've lost something
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新鲜海马奶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fresh seahorse milk
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.97,0:07:12.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:12.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有一种好像忘记了什么的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ever feel like you're forgetting something?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something important?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.85,0:07:25.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该跟这个食盆有点关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:25.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it has something to do with this bowl
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗的食盆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary's food bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,674)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.94,0:07:29.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:29.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.61,0:07:30.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得喂小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:30.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta feed Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才放几个小时  灰尘就积这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of dust for a couple of hours
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗快来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Soup's on
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.88,0:07:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pat?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.22,0:07:51.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:51.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我接受肮脏泡泡的挑战有多长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long was I taking the Dirty Bubble challenge?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.64,0:07:55.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概一周了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:55.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,About a week
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.89,0:07:56.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一周了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:56.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A week?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真这么久吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.81,0:07:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:07:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.49,0:08:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  大概一周
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's about a week
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也可能十天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,maybe ten days
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten days?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.74,0:08:18.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:18.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.08,0:08:26.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:26.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找不到小蜗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't find Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这办法肯定行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This never fails
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗最爱的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary's favorite treats
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证可以吸引小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary can't resist these babies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面装满了八种有机成分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're filled with eight types of organic sediment
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗这种底栖生物吃了还会想再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that bottom feeders like Gary can't get enough of
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.58,0:09:07.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有八种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:07.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eight?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要摇一摇罐子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you really have to do is shake the can
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗每次听到都会跑过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary comes running every time
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.63,0:09:13.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:13.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.38,0:09:13.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:13.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.93,0:09:16.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来摇摇看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:16.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样  这可是全新的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand, this is a brand-new
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.81,0:09:26.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只吃出来六种有机成分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:26.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I only tasted six types of sediment
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, where are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.57,0:09:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这下面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you under here?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续摇  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep shaking, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.36,0:09:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那两个野蛮人又在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are those Neanderthals up to?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道我忙着在享受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't they know I'm busy spoiling myself?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你去那边找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You check over there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这里面找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll check in here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Find him yet, Pat?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没找到  我会继续找的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, but I'll keep looking
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.86,0:10:12.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是已经没别的地方可以找了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:12.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But there's nowhere left to look
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有一个地方还没有找过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's one place we haven't checked
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗应该塞不进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I doubt Gary could fit in there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱看就看呗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't hurt to look
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(504,782)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来碰个运气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here goes nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.12,0:10:24.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:24.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.79,0:10:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看写了啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dear SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.33,0:10:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽管过去几年是我一生最美好的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:28.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These last few years have been
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some of the best of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是我必须要远走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I must move on
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用麻烦你过来找我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't bother to come looking for me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我可能已经找到了新主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By now, I have probably found a new owner
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.26,0:10:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能记得帮我装好食盆喂我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who actually remembers to fill up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my food bowl every now and again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗谨上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sincerely, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.30,0:10:47.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少这名字要用到新主人给我取名前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:47.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least until my new owner renames me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dear Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你几个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你赶人家走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You drove him away
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这上边白纸黑字清清楚楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's right there in black and white
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.15,0:10:54.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:54.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.94,0:10:55.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:55.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1118,210)}最后一家\N咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,468)}酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(850,468)}食物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(342,258)}睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678,116)}吃
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我裤子穿太高了吗  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are my pants too high, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:31.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(558,752)}玉米片
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看是谁来蹭饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look who came to dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那位应该不喜欢玉米片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess he didn't like nachos
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老奶奶可终于找见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gramma finally found you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人家都开始担心起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She was starting to get worried
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们回家去吧  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's get to your home, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.94,0:12:18.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你吃点好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:18.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get you something to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.73,0:12:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你比老奶奶印象里的还要轻得多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You feel much lighter than Gramma remembers
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好坐  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.66,0:12:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老奶奶知道你要电热毯毯舒服暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gramma knows you like your Mr. Heaty set to extra cozy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来陪你在家放松
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you're home relaxing
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.92,0:12:39.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  你饼干就要吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:39.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodness, you're almost out of cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去再拿一点来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll go and get some more
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不可以再偷跑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, don't you go running off again
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.47,0:12:51.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:51.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃完后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After this
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.06,0:12:56.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先前说好要做的恶魔蛋会再去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:56.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go make up some of those deviled eggs I promised
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来点音乐怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a little music?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老奶奶家的音响可厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gramma's got a killer stereo system
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.83,0:13:14.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这首歌让老奶奶想起了做铆工的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:14.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This song reminds Gramma of her days as a riveter
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你让老奶奶感觉年轻了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You make Gramma feel so young
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.85,0:13:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来跳点布吉伍吉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do the boogie-woogie
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:32.06,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 布吉伍吉：一种音乐风格 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  布吉伍吉跳够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough of the boogie-woogie for now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1008,876)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:47.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,388)}帽子
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(804,218)}饥饿蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(810,706)}蜗牛粮
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.83,0:13:55.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老奶奶知道你有多爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gramma knows how much you love
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.05,0:14:11.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些深夜犯罪剧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:11.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,these late-night crime drama programs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.30,0:14:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不对  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you, Miss Tuffsy?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  这么晩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heavens, look at the time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该睡觉了  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for bed, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道我在忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see I'm busy?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你房间到了  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your room, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡吧  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you are, darling
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老奶奶来给你盖被子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let Gramma tuck you in
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘了给你亲一下道晩安了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot your good night kiss
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你好梦  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,478)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.23,0:15:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你迟到了十五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're 15 minutes late
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一整晩都在外头找小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was out all night looking for Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道吗  小蜗离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, he ran away and
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now I
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.62,0:15:14.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:14.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看起来有点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look kinda
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.24,0:15:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,different
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.87,0:15:20.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说不上没事  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:20.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not exactly what you'd call okay, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.00,0:15:21.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道吗  我家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, my
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只是忘了戴帽子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just forgot to put your hat on
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.88,0:15:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就知道能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knew I'd figure it out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.26,0:15:35.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  我要退了这个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:35.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd like a refund for this Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.89,0:15:36.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:36.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Refund?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.89,0:15:37.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:37.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing, really
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是上面全是眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,except that it's covered in tears
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.81,0:15:43.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:43.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.73,0:15:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  外面还有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's customers out there, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.69,0:15:50.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着要吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:50.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,waiting to be fed
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.86,0:15:52.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不是我第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This wouldn't be the first time
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让某个挨饿的失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I disappointed someone who was hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你跟蟹老板说说出了什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell Mr. Krabs what's wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you see
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说够了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实  重要的不总是你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, its not always what you say that matters
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时  是你没说出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, it's what you don't say
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.42,0:16:08.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:08.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本该告诉小蜗在我心中有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should've told Gary how important he was to me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道这事跟做蟹黄堡有何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know what that has to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:14.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,making Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是我很清楚一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I do know this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any problem you have
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要努力工作  即可迎刃而解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can be solved with a little hard work
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才像话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's me boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果我要找到小蜗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to find Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要加倍努力去找才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need to work harder at it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界末日到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the apocalypse
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,办公用品从天上掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Office products falling from the sky
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是这样  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.66,0:16:42.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得用这些东西去找小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:42.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to use this stuff to go find Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明明就是你赶走小蜗的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I thought you drove him away
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.92,0:16:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不把小蜗当一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with your neglect and indifference
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.42,0:16:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  现在不是说闲话的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, now is not the time for talking
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有任务在身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got work to do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你喝  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新鲜现挤的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fresh squeezed
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.09,0:16:58.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然用挤的会比较久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:58.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It takes longer to make it that way
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这可都是我为爱做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it was a labor of love
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.22,0:17:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煎饼上面再多撒点糖浆怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a little more syrup on those pancakes?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火车过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes the train
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.15,0:17:15.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好玩一场吧  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:15.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Set phasers on fun, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,162)}玛莎手工店
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.58,0:17:22.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:22.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we are
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:28.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(670,254)}促销\N仅限今日
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个地方好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's a good spot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.92,0:17:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.59,0:17:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please come home
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱你的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧的  胶带给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, hand me the tape
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:38.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,226)}促销\N仅限今日
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.76,0:17:38.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,店里在做香薰松果大促销
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:38.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're having a sale on scented pine cones
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  现在不是做这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, this is no time for that
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pine cones
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.68,0:17:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种做手工用的绒条挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These pipe cleaners are simply delightful
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.69,0:17:50.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老太太  你赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:50.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old lady, quick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在找香薰松果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for the scented pine cones
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你不是因为要买才来找的  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you weren't looking to buy them, sonny
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.74,0:18:00.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为老奶奶已经全部都买走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:18:00.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because Gramma already picked up all they had
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你和我又要再一次分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once again, you and I are kept apart
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱的香薰松果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,O sweet scented pine cones
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.91,0:18:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.96,0:18:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把传单拿了发出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just take these fliers and hand them out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:16.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.76,0:18:19.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有好多好玩的事情可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:19.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's plenty more fun to be had
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(286,240)}小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(606,610)}我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(984,484)}爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,684)}你
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, now I know
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(250,300)}求你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(646,188)}回家
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I messed up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:27.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1158,878)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now you're gone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(742,160)}美发                                                              美甲
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.90,0:18:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗我对不起忽视了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, I'm sorry I neglected you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.28,0:18:38.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没有想过你会远走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:38.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, I never expected you to run away
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.49,0:18:42.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我感到如此的空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:42.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and leave me feeling this empty
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(716,830)}小蜗\N求你回家吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.53,0:18:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的喵声现在对我而言好似天籁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your meow right now would sound like music to me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please come home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我想你  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause I miss you, Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:56.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(818,622)}小蜗  求你回家吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.88,0:18:56.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:56.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, come home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗你可曾知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, can't you see
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:00.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(708,184)}茶店
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我太迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was blind
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿付出一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(506,112)}电器
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.43,0:19:04.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你心意改
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:04.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to change your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:05.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,324)}小蜗回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,796)}相簿
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不单是宠物  还是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More than a pet, you're my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美妙难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,too cool to forget
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来吧  我们是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come back 'cause we are family
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.28,0:19:21.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原谅我从前害你离家去流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:21.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and forgive me for making you wanna roam
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.91,0:19:27.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在的心正跳着那最悲伤的节拍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:27.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now my heart is beating like the saddest metronome
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.66,0:19:30.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你正在某处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:30.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Somewhere I hope you're reading
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.58,0:19:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,念着我刚写的短诗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my latest three-word poem
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(326,436)}小蜗\N回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:38.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(220,590)}小蜗\N回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1162,406)}丽莎\N嫁给我好吗
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, come home
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要花生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want peanuts
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, come home
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个丽莎到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who is this 'Lisa' person?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.02,0:19:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.56,0:19:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老奶奶要从烤箱那拿肉糕给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gramma will get a lovely meat loaf in the oven for you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.27,0:20:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了  不麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:20:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's no trouble at all
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy to do
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.49,0:20:07.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肥肥小妹  你要拉粑粑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:07.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Miss Tuffsy, do you have to go potty?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.08,0:20:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不就拉在这一大叠传单上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, why don't you use this stack of fliers
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.27,0:20:13.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是今天一个小胖墩给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:13.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,given to me today by a little chubby boy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(882,320)}亲爱的小蜗\N我很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(468,932)}求你回到我身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,300)}有没有看到小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\a3\pos(610,998)}看到的话就说我爱他\N海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(780,882)}小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,826)}小蜗\N求你回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1112,756)}小蜗\N我好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:20.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(546,194)}小蜗你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:20.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1192,290)}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(552,580)}小蜗回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1088,280)}小蜗\N我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  求你回到我身边来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, please come back to me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.10,0:20:28.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发吧  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:28.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, boy, go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.47,0:20:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待在那别动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You stay right there
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉糕就快做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The meatloaf is almost done
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.11,0:20:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉糕现在还没有准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The meatloaf is not quite ready yet
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.78,0:20:52.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是老奶奶知道你有多饿  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:52.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but Gramma knows how hungry you are, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.46,0:20:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以人家做好了一小盘饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so she whipped up a quick batch of cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不想要饼干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't want cookies?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't fret
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.44,0:21:17.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还做了一盘恶魔蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:17.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made a batch of deviled eggs, too
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.61,0:21:20.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:20.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.15,0:21:22.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可以浪费这些吃的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:22.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't want these to go to waste, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是我为爱做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They were a labor of love
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.07,0:21:28.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.07,0:21:28.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老奶奶会找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gramma will find you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.33,0:21:34.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是不喜欢玉米片的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:34.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the guy that doesn't like nachos
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.46,0:21:37.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肥肥小妹  我知道你在那后头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:37.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Miss Tuffsy, I know you're back there
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都能听到你肚子叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can hear your stomach growling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.55,0:21:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊  肥肥小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, Miss Tuffsy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.01,0:21:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.84,0:21:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定是饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be starving
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都发泄出来吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just let it out, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.06,0:21:57.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:57.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也哭不出来了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't cry anymore, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.40,0:22:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗一走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When Gary left
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.61,0:22:03.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也一并带走了我的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:03.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He took all my tears with him
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚说到小蜗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you just say Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:06.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.95,0:22:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我记起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just remembered
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.11,0:22:10.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天早些时候我在手工店里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:10.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Earlier today at the craft store
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.74,0:22:14.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好大块的木块
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:14.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,these huge chunks of balsa wood
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.41,0:22:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,质量可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They were awesome
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.00,0:22:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗喜欢木块
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary loved balsa wood
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.58,0:22:22.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得把小蜗忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:22.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to try to forget Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.05,0:22:27.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是不知为何  我就是忘不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:27.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I can't get him out of my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:28.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(718,638)}你有见到我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.05,0:22:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I blew it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.14,0:22:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I really blew it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.72,0:22:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我之前没把你当一回事  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I took you for granted, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.81,0:22:35.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:35.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.27,0:22:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别光这样瞪我  快说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't just stare at me, say something
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.48,0:22:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在跟广告牌讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to a billboard
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.19,0:22:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在还幻听了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm hearing things
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.94,0:22:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我能再见到你一次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only I could see you one more time
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.90,0:22:49.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我就能再告诉你  我有多爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:49.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I could tell you how much I love you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.41,0:22:53.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能再听到你喵一声就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:53.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only I could hear you meow one last time
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.66,0:22:56.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就像是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:56.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like that
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.66,0:23:00.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你的呼噜声让我更难忘掉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:00.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, your purring is making it hard to forget you
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.83,0:23:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.83,0:23:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.84,0:23:07.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你刚刚有没有听到那番话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.84,0:23:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, did you hear any of that
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.72,0:23:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需不需要再重复给你讲一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or do I have to repeat myself?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.76,0:23:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.76,0:23:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, good
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.64,0:23:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.22,0:23:15.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会再像之前那样子对你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:15.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Things are going to be different between you and I
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.60,0:23:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll see, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.02,0:23:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回家给你点东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's go home and get you something to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.14,0:23:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定是饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be starving
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.23,0:23:27.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道是哪出了错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:27.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how things went so wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.82,0:23:34.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我转过身小蜗不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:34.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I turned around and he was gone
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.78,0:23:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.49,0:23:41.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每晩我向小蜗的空床扪心自问
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:41.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Each night I ask his empty bed
Dialogue: 1,0:23:41.12,0:23:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我说了错话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was it something that I said?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.25,0:23:47.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脑袋里的小声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:47.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The little voice inside my head
Dialogue: 1,0:23:47.09,0:23:49.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说小蜗去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:49.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,says "Where has Gary gone?”
